    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Weapon (Any Simple or Martial), Rare</em></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\">When you attack a creature with this magic weapon and roll a 20 on the attack roll, that target takes an extra 3d6 necrotic damage, provided that the target isn't a construct or an undead. You gain temporary hit points equal to the extra damage dealt.</span></p><p>Midi: To use the item simply drag the Life Stealer effect to any weapon and it will do extra damage when a natural 20 is rolled.</p><p>This is based on a idea from the new Dungeons Master's Guide foundry premium content which has lots of clever ideas in it.</p>",
